+### Test 5: Summary tab
+
+1. Switch to "Summary" page tab
+2. **Expect**: Form E-mapped sections showing captured data
+3. **Expect**: Hero financial numbers (assets, liabilities, income, outgoings)
+4. **Expect**: Gaps section showing what's missing
